Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.52,0:50:09.99,OP -2,NTP,0,0,0,,Wake Up! 把祈祷传达出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.28,0:50:16.75,OP -2,NTP,0,0,0,,现在伸出双手 实现理想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.94,0:50:22.41,OP -2,NTP,0,0,0,,Stand Up! 毫无迷惘的奔跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.66,0:50:28.60,OP -2,NTP,0,0,0,,为了在这世界活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.80,0:50:31.08,OP -2,NTP,0,0,0,,与你一起
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.22,0:50:35.73,OP -2,NTP,0,0,0,,My only one
